data.text: John Meillon was born on May 1, 1934 in Mosman, Sydney, New South Wales, Australia. He was an actor and writer, known for Crocodile Dundee II (1988), Crocodile Dundee - Ein Krokodil zum Küssen (1986) and Walkabout - Der Traum vom Leben (1971). He was married to Bunny Gibson and June Salter. He died on August 10, 1989 in Neutral Bay, Sydney, New South Wales, Australia.
